<!--
  Wheeled Dual UR5e V2

  Purpose:
    A cleaner four-wheel dual-arm mobile manipulator MJCF for visualization,
    kinematic MPC, and Pinocchio FK/Jacobian checks.

  Compatibility:
    - Keeps the same 16 actuated DOFs and joint names as wheeled_dual_ur5e.xml:
        base_x, base_y, base_yaw, base_z,
        left_* six arm joints,
        right_* six arm joints.
    - Keeps left_ee_site / right_ee_site and left/right target mocap names.
    - Wheels are high-quality visual geometry in this version. They intentionally
      do not add wheel joints, so the existing dual-arm MPC code remains 16-DOF.

  Geometry concept:
    Four-wheel mobile base + top deck + fixed mast + moving lift carriage +
    two side-by-side UR5e-style arms on shoulder pedestals.
-->
